#text
<strong>: important
- <b>: bold
<em>: emphasized
- <i>: italic
<mark>: highlighted
<code>: monospace
<br>: line break
<wbr>: possible line break
<hr>: horizontal line
<sup>: superscript
<sub>: subscript
<small>: smaller

#core
<html>: root element
<head>: metadata before body
<body>: content
<footer>: after body

#structure
<h1>-<h6>: headings
<article>: self-contained content
<p>: paragraph
<table>: columns and rows
- <caption>
- <thead>
- <tbody>
- <tfoot>
- <tr>: row in table
- <td>: cell in row
- <th>: header cell
<ul>: unordered list
<ol>: ordered list
- reversed
- start: number
- type: 1 | A | a | I | i
<li>: list item
<dl>: description list
- <dt>: term
- <dd>: description
<div>: block section
<span>: inline section
<details>: closable content
- <summary>: title of closable content
- open: initial state

#content
<a>: hyperlink
- href: path
- target: _self | _blank (new tab) | _parent (iframe) | _top (new window)
<img>: picture
- alt: text
- src: path
- width
- height
<ruby>: text with pronunciation
- <rt>: pronunciation (above)
<iframe>: embed document

#other
abbr: abbreviation
address: contact info
blockquote: quotation
- cite: source
q: short quotation

#global attributes
class: style
id: unique name
style: inline CSS
title: tooltip
lang: 2-letter code
translate: yes | no
contenteditable
draggable
hidden
inert: disable
tabindex: order in tab navigation
